            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8E%E8%82%A9%23&amp;extparam=%232%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8E%E8%82%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#2个动作改善高低肩#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打工人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2023_earner_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】长时间伏案可能导致高低肩，学习两个动作：①背靠墙，双臂伸直，缓慢举到头顶，再缓慢放下，每天做50下左右；②手背到身后，背挺直，手缓慢抬高，再缓慢放下，每天做20下左右。不想高低肩影响仪态的朋友练起来👇🏻（浙大邵逸夫医院骨科徐文斌） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4923016644329514" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hfv5rorz7gj60k00zkdhw02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/SueV8WZ7lx086Yl4JxpC01041200ivJu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689282823&amp;ssig=rjc%2BW9Zxol&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/HI7fwKq4lx086Yl55C0w01041200bnqh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689282823&amp;ssig=HK0cZPck5Y&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5wCFy5EGlx086Yl4l9du010412006tZc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689282823&amp;ssig=m1VwOLuyQu&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4923016644329514&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
